      • isGhostClose

        public double isGhostClose(GhostsList gl)
        this method returns the azimuth from the player to a close ghost. if there is no ghost closer than 4 meters to the player, the azimuth remains -1. if there is a ghost less than 4 meters from the player, it calculates the azimuth between them, and return it.
        Parameters:
        gl: - the given ghosts list.
